{"tid":1708202,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"老蕭又中,前兩日講過王思聰炫富,今日傳出被限制高消費","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T13:38:25.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fb727bfef310f0bd736fbd740d3ef68bc24a2d68","tid":1708202,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8XMos_XW-FQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8XMos_XW-FQ&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQQmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=ac310570\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8XMos_XW-FQ</a><br />\n<br />\n王思聰被限制高消費 普思投資：全力應對有解決方案<br />\n11月11日消息，普思投資聲明稱，近期網絡關於普思投資董事長王思聰先生被列為被執行人，限制高消費報導，是因為熊貓電視直播平台倒閉而引發的投資糾紛。目前普思投資代表王思聰先生正在全力應對，已有解決方案，我們完全有能力盡快自己解決問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWMJqtW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWMJqtW.jpg&h=58351560&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}